comment: /**  * Resolve the given destination name, either as located resource  * or as dynamic destination.  * @param session the current JMS Session  * (may be {@code null} if the resolver implementation is able to work without it)  * @param destinationName the name of the destination  * @param pubSubDomain {@code true} if the domain is pub-sub, {@code false} if P2P  * @return the JMS destination (either a topic or a queue)  * @throws javax.jms.JMSException if the JMS Session failed to resolve the destination  * @throws DestinationResolutionException in case of general destination resolution failure  */
code: /**  * Resolve the given destination name, either as located resource  * or as dynamic destination.  * @param session the current JMS Session  * (may be {@code null} if the resolver implementation is able to work without it)  * @param destinationName the name of the destination  * @param pubSubDomain {@code true} if the domain is pub-sub, {@code false} if P2P  * @return the JMS destination (either a topic or a queue)  * @throws javax.jms.JMSException if the JMS Session failed to resolve the destination  * @throws DestinationResolutionException in case of general destination resolution failure  */ Destination resolveDestinationName(@Nullable Session session, String destinationName, boolean pubSubDomain) throws JMSException.
